    "The primary goal of the developed AH-CNN-Res-LSTM technique is to improve the MCC and decrease the FDR in predicting human motion intentions.At last, different performance computations are performed in the suggested framework to examine the prediction efficiency over different metrics.",
    "The architectural illustration of the developed human motion intention prediction model with the deep learning model is represented in Fig. 1.",
    "Human motion intention datasetIn the developed multimodal data-based human motion intention prediction model, EEG/EMG signals and sensor measures are used for the validation, and their details are listed below.EEG/EMG Signals: Here, the signals are collected from the dataset named HumanAct12 39.",
    "This dataset holds the polar image with a 3D pose and images with temporal cropping.",
    "The dataset has 1191 3D motion clips, which are classified into 12 different action classes as well as 34 sub-classes."
